  <summary date="2017-01-10T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Veterans Choice Continuation Act

This bill amends the Veterans Access, Choice, and Accountability Act of 2014 to eliminate the August 7, 2017, termination date for the Veterans Choice Program, which allows the program to operate until all of the money in the Veterans Choice Fund is expended.</summary>
